task.summary: - fix unittest - Adds WeakReference for better memory footprint.
- start derby db server as network service - Implements the RESTFul service.
- Dashboard build. - Dashboard spark RESTful ready.
- Unittest fix. - Adds Dashboard launcher. - Updates copyright for Web files. - Modify the build and launch script to make it one click show.
- Regression test fixes. - Batch improvement on options.
- Adds MySQL / Postgres support for Dashboard - Improve stability of Dashboard experience.
- adds initial design / implementation of project association.
- Initial version of project association. - CSV upload functionality.
- First step to integrate DC parser.
- Avoid overhead index creation. - Improve Violation export performance.
- Adds test cases for incremental inserting.
Adds qatar living vehicles dataset (adds csv data).
- Adds support for boolean and datetime type. - Fix bugs in the Dashboard, adds DC support. - Adds extra interface for violation query (rule name matching and violation limit).

- Adds initial framework for test app of qatar car sales. - Adds Guava 15.0 support. - Clean the project deps. - Adds exception handler for rule detect / repair itself. - Adds better Log4j support (-Ddebug). - Minor bug fixes.
